Description: This data set contains 10,000 cloned Github repos that contain Android app source files.

This data set contains 134 execution traces consisting of initializing events, callbacks, and framework callins on running Android applications. In these traces, 184 distinct Android types have been traced.
This data set consists of scraped Google Code Jam submissions from 2006 through 2015, restricted to those written in C and compilable using ‘gcc -c‘ with gcc version 4.6.4.
